{"tid":397250,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［張國榮生忌］如果哥哥未死，今年已經六十一歲","createTime":"2017-09-12T10:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T04:53:32.000Z","uid":35639,"like":46,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb214f1cdc467bb35544e36ebb286d1266d1f155","tid":397250,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"一個受咁多人愛戴 外表咁討好既人 加上種自戀同高傲<br />\n會唔會其實一直都諗住 live fast, die young and leave a good-looking corpse<br />\n諗諗下如果自己咁靚仔都未必接受到第時老態龍鍾既狀態<br />\n老左醜左都同而家無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6880dcd5e2a2e7f4e45a356c2679670cf4553c23","tid":397250,"uid":95761,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:58:57.000Z","msg":"我永遠都咁愛你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢真係好獨一無二既明星<br />\n由性格到演技到外表<br />\n舉手投足都令我覺得佢唔似一個凡人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢溝死唔知幾多女既同時 連仔都俾佢吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢簡直就係一件藝術品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdc564b293561bbc4b821417197592c1388ae8e","tid":397250,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"Dorian Grey<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bb993135b7abd52dadbb7fece8ec2f47a51292","tid":397250,"uid":55217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"好掛住哥哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae730bc03e5902beb0f76bc3d1fcb56ff22f9de4","tid":397250,"uid":28068,"like":5,"d